00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:12.180
that we have to read the Bible

00:00:12.180 --> 00:00:15.479
and how God has revealed himself to us

00:00:15.479 --> 00:00:17.100
through the pages of scripture.

00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.780
